## Installation

```bash
pip install botwit
```

### Developper

##### Install

```bash
make install
```

##### Launch tests:

```bash
pytest
```

##### Write docs:

```bash
mkdocs serve --watch .
```

### Update Cookiecutter Template

```bash
cruft update --skip-apply-ask --allow-untracked-files --project-dir .
```
